var(--youcolor);&quot;]]<br />\n怎麼了？<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;clear: left;&quot;]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;me&quot; data-kidoku=&quot;已讀&quot; data-time=&quot;14:31&quot;]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;talk&quot; style=&quot;background-color: var(--mecolor);&quot;]]<br />\n10分鐘前有個保安人員被送來醫護室<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;clear: right;&quot;]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;me&quot; data-kidoku=&quot;已讀&quot; data-time=&quot;14:32&quot;]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;talk&quot; style=&quot;background-color: var(--mecolor);&quot;]]<br />\n他的耳朵和右眼不見了<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;clear: right;&quot;]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;icon&quot;]]<br />\n[[image https://i.imgur.com/KYyLuk4.jpg]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;you&quot; data-time=&quot;14:34&quot;]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;talk&quot;&nbsp;&nbsp;style=&quot;background-color: var(--youcolor);&quot;]]<br />\n收容失效了？<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;clear: left;&quot;]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;me&quot; data-kidoku=&quot;已讀&quot; data-time=&quot;14:37&quot;]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;talk&quot; style=&quot;background-color: var(--mecolor);&quot;]]<br />\n沒有<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;clear: right;&quot;]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;icon&quot;]]<br />\n[[image https://i.imgur.com/KYyLuk4.jpg]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;you&quot; data-time=&quot;14:38&quot;]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;talk&quot;&nbsp;&nbsp;style=&quot;background-color: var(--youcolor);&quot;]]<br />\n他剛才在做什麼？<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[div style=&quot;clear: left;&quot;]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;me&quot; data-kidoku=&quot;已讀&quot; data-time=&quot;14:39&quot;]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;talk&quot; style=&quot;background-color: var(--mecolor);&q